 you up</blockquote><br />\n你係咪on 9 架，查字典啦"},{"pid":"33dd65cba1a9e8d91d357bc23096a8ad1a5dc294","tid":370794,"uid":44301,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T06:32:26.000Z","msg":"咁多人話比普通市民睇 依家有中文喎<br />\n咁即係話英文其實係比外國人睇啦<br />\n但你地有冇諗過外國人睇唔睇得明依啲港式英語先"},{"pid":"bfc1c1ec45ba76c9a05ef2c874ca91423d8c2548","tid":370794,"uid":41818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T06:33:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁多人話比普通市民睇 依家有中文喎<br />\n咁即係話英文其實係比外國人睇啦<br />\n但你地有冇諗過外國人睇唔睇得明依啲港式英語先</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1db585126698a45a59d3dd9edd3e5f90b08c180d","tid":370794,"uid":41791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T06:34:03.000Z","msg":"負皮代表一切"},{"pid":"6ca3edaf4635c1346b1fbe94560408ce536d34c0","tid":370794,"uid":34759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T06:34:14.000Z","msg":"可唔可以去平機會向警署犯罪定性"},{"pid":"84aff8bd843fecd696421f8b050cd095bdb345af","tid":370794,"uid":34759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T06:37:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可唔可以去平機會告警署犯罪定性</blockquote>"},{"pid":"67df389c9ff83b61b24a5ec0621043db3778ce75","tid":370794,"uid":61994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T06:40:10.000Z","msg":"中文版係咪要寫文言文先可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"c02c09c4cb3b654079ea2860708d5f4ad1fc1d1c","tid":370794,"uid":113456,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T06:40:54.000Z","msg":"唔係話poster一定要咁樣 但如果要寫靚d我會咁寫 有錯請指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1. Do not flaunt your valuables in public / Keep your valuables from plain sight(不過呢個多用於旅行)<br />\n<br />\n2. Do not take shortcuts, stick to busy streets with a lot of lighting<br />\n<br />\n3. Have someone you trust to pick you up after a late night out<br />\n<br />\n4. Call the police and go somewhere crowded if you think you are being followed<br />\n<br />\n利申 覺得本身真係夠簡單易明 但如果畀英語為母語既人睇一定會覺得奇奇怪怪 不過香港確實有其他唔識睇中文 而英文又唔係超級高水平既人 例如少數族裔/外國遊客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  整呢張poster既人應該有考慮過呢點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58282ee0859882429cc21a95d4b42bda0ca65e38","tid":370794,"uid":38548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T06:45:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Ask your family to meet you <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇得改好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAsk someone to pick you up</blockquote><br />\n你係咪on 9 架，查字典啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 對唔住大師<br />\n<br />\n字典話pick up 係解執起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c178f817f1827574ac0aa50a44b1d3a1ef025c7b","tid":370794,"uid":57480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T07:02:15.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得無乜問題，明就得。<br />\n<br />\nDon't show off your valuables.<br />\n<br />\nAvoid short cuts in lonely areas. Keep to well-lit, busy streets.<br />\n<br />\nHave someone you trust to walk you home at night.<br />\n<br />\nIf you think you&rsquo;re being followed, walk to the busiest place you can find. Then call the police"},{"pid":"ee862b984e3a6eb999e62799e2882116034bb52f","tid":370794,"uid":26432,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T07:04:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/23/164233_a14d58c5c1f35e01e41ebcc0d6a3eaa1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F23%2F164233_a14d58c5c1f35e01e41ebcc0d6a3eaa1.jpg&h=1882b735&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第3, 4點我會譯做咁樣:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3. Ask for family's company (or pick-up) if you stay out late</span><br />\n屌你點會用come home late架? 你用go home late都算啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">4. Get to the crowd when suspecting being followed</span><br />\n英文D sign通常好簡單同埋避免使用逗號</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啱啱考完DSE? com咩pany, 你寫呢啲咁啲巴基睇條撚咩<br />\n<br />\nHave your family pick you up late at night<br />\n<br />\nGet to the crowd if you are being followed<br />\n<br />\n簡單易明<br />\n<br />\n嗰啲咩<span style=\"color: red;\">request company from whom you trust 呀, divert to the crowd should you feel being tailed</span> 就考試先拎黎獻世la</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你的兩句例子都好, 但我冇撚考過DSE, COMPANY呢個字都唔係咁難姐下馬?<br />\n<br />\n利申: IELTS全部band 8.0+"},{"pid":"378cbda41fbb9ef3b13ae6f5b4dcdd2a74643e32","tid":370794,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T07:09:43.000Z","msg":"你地係度blame the victim! 叫女權撚出黎!"},{"pid":"5113c4577081b43e2f5bc344dd828ec3b1015f3d","tid":370794,"uid":18384,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T07:15:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.police.gov.sg/~/media/spf/images/crimeposter/outrage%20of%20modesty_a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.sg%2F~%2Fmedia%2Fspf%2Fimages%2Fcrimeposter%2Foutrage%2520of%2520modesty_a3.jpg&h=a7bb4114&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9bf0bd3afb8eb46c9f73bb536f083b5d2fccdc50","tid":370794,"uid":106468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,