one you trust to walk you home at night.<br />\n<br />\nIf you think you&rsquo;re being followed, walk to the busiest place you can find. Then call the police</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打改得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nStaying safe from robbery<br />\n<br />\nIf you have to walk alone at night take extra care. Stay on roads that are well lit and relatively busy<br />\nPlan your route in advance<br />\nAvoid short cuts that involve alleyways or walking across parks or commons unless they are well-lit<br />\nIf you're carrying a bag, try to have it across your chest and keep your hand over the fastening<br />\nBe aware of your surroundings and stay alert to what's going on around you<br />\nBe careful with your electronics; talking on a mobile phone, listening to an MP3 player or carrying a laptop bag shows thieves that you have something to steal<br />\nDon't carry important documents or credit cards that you do not need<br />\nOnly take your wallet out when you need to<br />\nIf you think you are being followed, cross the road or go into a shop and stay there until you're sure you're safe<br />\n<br />\nFrom UK Police Force <a href=\"https://www.police.uk/crime-prevention-advice/theft-and-robbery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.uk%2Fcrime-prevention-advice%2Ftheft-and-robbery%2F&d=MZbb6wOW8NUOP6KiUv6%2B8Mn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=05fb77eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.uk/crime-prevention-advice/theft-and-robbery/</a>"},{"pid":"6a44ab5fc6eae3840dbb99c6676f550a58d22b92","tid":370794,"uid":35587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T09:09:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/23/164233_a14d58c5c1f35e01e41ebcc0d6a3eaa1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F23%2F164233_a14d58c5c1